    <item>
      <title>米雷：与中国的贸易并不“与共产党结盟”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/milei-trade-with-china-isn-t-aligning-with-communists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在接受彭博新闻社主编约翰·米克尔思韦特的独家采访时，阿根廷自由党总统哈维尔·米莱放弃了对中国这一阿根廷最大贸易伙伴和债权人的批评。就在去年，他将中国描述为一个“凶残的政权”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/milei-trade-with-china-isn-t-aligning-with-communists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 23:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储卡什卡里认为 2024 年可能不降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/fed-s-kashkari-sees-possibility-of-no-rate-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明尼阿波利斯联邦储备银行行长尼尔·卡什卡里 (Neel Kashkari) 表示，如果通胀进展在 LinkedIn 的虚拟活动中停滞不前，今年可能不需要降息。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/fed-s-kashkari-sees-possibility-of-no-rate-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 23:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度如何赢得中国的增长桂冠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/how-india-can-win-china-s-growth-crown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国经济正在放缓，而印度正在争夺全球最大增长动力的地位。但道路上充满了障碍。印度在夺取中国的桂冠之前需要解决什么问题？ （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/how-india-can-win-china-s-growth-crown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅斯特称美联储接近降息信心水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/mester-says-fed-close-to-confidence-level-for-cuts-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰联邦储备银行行长洛雷塔·梅斯特表示，央行可能已经接近在未来几个月开始降息所需的信心水平。她在全球相互依存中心主办的在线讨论中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/mester-says-fed-close-to-confidence-level-for-cuts-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:47:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在就业数据和石油上涨之前，股市面临压力：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率不确定性和地缘政治紧张局势打压市场情绪，亚洲股市周五早盘跟随美国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛薪酬计划遭遇阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/goldman-sachs-pay-plan-sees-pushback-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家著名的代理咨询公司要求股东投票反对高盛集团的高管薪酬计划，此前这家华尔街巨头的高层领导人在利润下滑的一年里获得了大幅加薪。斯里·纳塔拉詹报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/goldman-sachs-pay-plan-sees-pushback-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ares 牵头 CentralSquare 12 亿美元再融资交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ares-leads-1-2-billion-refinancing-deal-for-centralsquare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，以 Ares Management Corp. 为首的私人信贷公司正在向软件开发商 CentralSquare Technologies 提供超过 12 亿美元的债务方案，为其债务再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ares-leads-1-2-billion-refinancing-deal-for-centralsquare</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
